reviews.review_text: Flacs are fried i just downloaded the flac files and all of them are nothing but hiss. I converted them to wave just to make sure and they too are all hiss. I have other copies of this show and its definitely a5 star. I'm giving this one the same 5 stars.

FLACs are fine Wow, Sammo.  Considering the insane amount of work that Dan Haugh went to in order to make these files available, the least you could do is read his notes before posting.  Just a hint, if you're experiencing technical issues with something put together by someone with Dan's skills, it's probably you.
